      <details class="group rounded-xl border border-[oklch(0.92_0.003_0)] bg-white overflow-hidden reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-ink cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-surface/50 transition-colors">
          ¿Puedo integrar Difunde con mi CRM?
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-muted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
